00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:06.519
Our ministry is another kind of search and rescue operation,

00:00:06.519 --> 00:00:10.019
and we search wherever people can be found.

00:00:10.019 --> 00:00:13.220
For example, in the following report,

00:00:13.220 --> 00:00:16.820
notice the efforts our brothers made to reach people

00:00:16.820 --> 00:00:24.199
living in the remotest areas of Africa.

00:00:24.199 --> 00:00:28.199
Jesus made the bold statement at X1, verse 8.

00:00:28.199 --> 00:00:30.199
You will be witnesses of me

00:00:30.199 --> 00:00:34.200
to the most distant parts of the earth.

00:00:34.299 --> 00:00:38.100
This resonates deeply in a country of Namibia.

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:40.899
This warm and beautiful people

00:00:40.899 --> 00:00:48.640
are spread across great expanses of dramatic and thirsty land.

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:52.539
The people are not only separated by physical distances,

00:00:52.539 --> 00:00:55.840
they also separate by cultures,

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:58.539
ancient traditions,

00:00:58.539 --> 00:01:02.240
and historic injustices.

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:04.540
Since a South Africa branch offers overseas

00:01:04.540 --> 00:01:06.640
the work in this territory,

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:10.239
we are pleased to assist a group of brothers

00:01:10.239 --> 00:01:12.140
from the capital city Vantuk

00:01:12.140 --> 00:01:14.640
with a special witnessing trip.

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:18.640
So brothers, our journey will start in Vantuk

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:21.439
and we're going to travel to Humph first.

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:23.840
From there, we're going to go to Tumquay.

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:27.439
We're going to camp in those two places, Hum and Tumquay.

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:32.140
And we may travel a distance of about 1,500 kilometers.

00:01:32.239 --> 00:01:34.340
Let's talk safety now.

00:01:34.340 --> 00:01:37.540
You want to keep three creatures out of your tent,

00:01:37.540 --> 00:01:41.939
animals such as Ahinas, scorpions, and snakes.

00:01:41.939 --> 00:01:44.239
Always the pure tent.

00:01:44.239 --> 00:01:47.239
Tonets facilities, a method

00:01:47.239 --> 00:01:50.239
