00:01:50.239 --> 00:01:53.239
When we enter the Herrera home,

00:01:53.239 --> 00:01:54.939
enter through the side gate.

00:01:54.939 --> 00:01:56.739
This is to show respect

00:01:56.739 --> 00:01:59.040
because they have areas in their homesteads

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:01.140
that are restricted for ancestor worship.

00:02:01.140 --> 00:02:03.840
